# Chase Analytics brand assets (four styles)
#
# 1. chase-icon-filled.png — icon-only purple curve (favicon, loading, compact accents)
# 2. chase-logo-horizontal.png — dark-theme horizontal wordmark (PRIMARY NAV / dark headers)
# 3. chase-logo-horizontal-light.png — light-bg horizontal wordmark (use inside .ca-brand-badge-light)
# 4. chase-logo-stacked-light.png — light-bg stacked wordmark (splash, reports, empty states — NOT nav)
#
# Legacy aliases (optional): chase-logo-transparent.png, chase-icon-outline.png
